{"tid":105620,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一段插畫師的訪問：Parsue Choi (ネコ憑き付き)","createTime":"2017-02-03T04:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T05:33:10.000Z","uid":44773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ddf10acbeace25ceb1541c553cc2898e70f4e49","tid":105620,"uid":44773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"所以精美的插畫版權是他本人所有，不便發佈，但大家可到他的網站瀏覽：<br />\n<a href=\"https://plus.google.com/+ParsueChoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplus.google.com%2F%2BParsueChoi&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=358fce30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://plus.google.com/+ParsueChoi</a><br />\n<br />\nP.46-49<br />\n//...手繪是從小就四處畫開始的，家中的牆上、學校的教科書上，只要有空位就畫<br />\n個滿滿的，在高中時代才開始正式練習基本功，以速寫為主；中學畢業(93)後已沒有怎<br />\n麼畫畫，在99年就職公司裡畫了三頁宣傳用的漫畫後就完全停筆了。因為各種原因放棄<br />\n了創作14年...//<br />\n<br />\n原圖文：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/andy729huiblog/posts/397029463980006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fandy729huiblog%2Fposts%2F397029463980006&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=199577be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/andy729huiblog/posts/397029463980006</a>"},{"pid":"771f3fc01eebebfb6757650e807a182c36cae30c","tid":105620,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"香港畫師能畫到這樣已經很好了<br />\n有p站？"},{"pid":"586e1bf9a993ca8e352b826467c21e25bee86bde","tid":105620,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:33:10.000Z","msg":"畫好過佢嘅插畫師大有人在<br />\n起碼自己身邊有一個先"}]}